Forked components (adapted): project-scope command/skill discovery,
$ARGUMENTS substitution and frontmatter parsing (command-content.ts,
discovery.ts), project-local config persistence (project-config.ts),
system prompt sections (system-prompt.ts), and the /claude-commands,
/claude-load, /claude-unload management commands.

New components: user-scope (~/.claude) discovery, Claude plugin discovery
(enabledPlugins + marketplace/cache root resolution), agent symlink sync,
and the Claude Code hooks bridge (extensions/claude-bridge/hooks/).
